data.description: Welcome to this Beautiful 2020 Built home with water views; Access to a private community pier as well as water front.   The home is wired for a 30 AMP RV as well as a level 2 EV.  You will have no problem parking your vehicles at this home which comes w an expansive two car garage and wide driveway suited for recreational vehicles.  The value goes beyond the double rear deck, expanded patio, new shed&greenhouse and newly added exterior features; All of these features are great,  but the true treasure your customer’s will admire is the open concept floor plan with energy efficient appliances, large open kitchen w island, contemporary bathrooms, the list is too expansive a visit will not disappoint.   When you do come, try to envision taking a bike ride or golf cart ride to the local waterfront restaurants and bars or simply to the pier.  This open concept coastal home will appeal to those looking for a functional home consolidated with  vacation like surroundings while providing quick access to Annapolis & DC!
